0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772421068}, {"pid": 859714760, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 29, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-02 11:16", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=859712858,45974302,1802]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65490615]子午卯酉甲乙丙丁[/uid] (2026-03-02 11:05):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大明天计划是等比例减，还是把活动仓位(资源，封测，光伏)减了啊[/quote]<br/>早上冲高不减你现在问我明天？我今早说的最多的就是冲高减仓。", "lou": 1002, "content_length": 63, "reply_to": 859712858, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772421406}, {"pid": 859716202, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 53, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-02 11:25", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=859518569,45974302,1764]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=150058]-阿狼-[/uid] (2026-02-28 15:42):[/b]<br/><br/>所以我周4周5减仓高位科技换到了低位科技 也就是本来我可能亏-10  现在最多-4 打个比方啊<br/>这样在加上我对冲的石油，我整体心态就会稳住 而不会胡乱操作<br/><br/>事件不会压死人，胡乱操作才会。<br/>[color=red]你想想有没有人是 周末定好周一开盘就割肉，或者隔夜单，开盘跑了后发现下杀没多久就有抄底的来反抽了，又作死追了进去，但是反抽资金只是偷鸡抄底做自救而已，马上就能T出，那他是不是套里面了。最后GJD救了指数没救他的方向。这样搞神仙都救不了的。[/color][/quote]<br/><br/>标红给你们看", "lou": 1003, "content_length": 17, "reply_to": 859518569, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772421909}, {"pid": 859718103, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 7, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-02 11:36", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=859716079,45974302,1803]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66586092]笔下山河[/uid] (2026-03-02 11:24):[/b]<br/><br/>感觉聚合材料可以高看一眼。周末围观了两天，小摩托无人机真是超预期。未来西大东大星链/北斗+ai，小摩托就是新时代的AK47了，希望泽子和佩子抗住，多创造点需求出来[img]./mon_202603/02/jmQ2x-8tx2ZjT3cShs-1hq.jpg[/img][/quote]<br/>你猜一下为啥你现在猜看到 聚合我目前翻倍盈利了[s:ac:哭笑]", "lou": 1004, "content_length": 47, "reply_to": 859716079, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772422586}, {"pid": 859728967, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 19, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-02 13:04", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=859727872,45974302,1806]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66758380]一路红K[/uid] (2026-03-02 12:53):[/b]<br/><br/>伊朗看来不打算谈判了，战争估计要持续一段时间，大家还是可以看看军工方面的，虽然今天有资金兑现，但我觉得还是能高看一眼。目前卖掉石油转军工了[s:ac:闪光][img]./mon_202603/02/jmQ2x-3r13ZdT1kShs-12w.jpg[/img][/quote]<br/>多余 石油肯定比军工强的。石油自己的逻辑都没走完", "lou": 1005, "content_length": 51, "reply_to": 859727872, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772427865}, {"pid": 859730434, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 26, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-02 13:18", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "正在目标4190中 可以期待一下", "lou": 1006, "content_length": 26, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772428699}, {"pid": 859731181, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 43, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-02 13:25", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "早上没减的  这次冲高我还是说  减到75%过开会", "lou": 1007, "content_length": 39, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772429106}, {"pid": 859731479, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 24, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-02 13:27", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=859731329,45974302,1809]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38754660]消费机的逆袭[/uid] (2026-03-02 13:26):[/b]<br/><br/>今天强硬的ai硬要减吗[/quote]<br/>你爱减啥减啥。我只说总体仓位<br/>我怎么知道你们有什么", "lou": 1008, "content_length": 53, "reply_to": 859731329, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772429257}, {"pid": 859732069, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 23, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-02 13:32", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=859731948,45974302,1809]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64492456]tkruthless[/uid] (2026-03-02 13:31):[/b]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202603/02/jmQ2x-5thfK4ToS6k-1i.jpg[/img]感谢石油王  有点想再贪明天 再吃一口石油 还是今天就跑 ？ 想要个建议[/quote]<br/>任何时候